SOMA Read Iterator Base class

SOMA Read Iterator Base class

Details

Class that allows for read iteration of SOMA reads.

Method read_next()

Read the next chunk of an iterated read. (lifecycle: maturing). If read is complete, retunrs NULL and raises warning.

Usage
